parameters: \nc<Producer>Oh, Saki-chan. Welcome. How are you? No changes?

\nc<Producer>You remember the other day, right? You know, when you
stopped by Saki-chan's house with me for work.

\nc<Producer>It seems they really liked the footage from that day. In the
end, they decided to switch completely to adult programming.
\nc<Producer>He found his goal, all thanks to you, Saki-chan!

\nc<Producer>Hm? What's wrong? You're making that face. Ah~ could it be
you're missing some physical affection? Hahaha!

\nc<Producer>If that's the case, don't worry. Actually, I called you here
because I have a favor to ask about him.

\nc<Producer>It's good that we moved platforms, but since the genre
changed, it seems we're struggling to gather new
subscribers.

\nc<Producer>That's where I thought of you, Saki-chan. What do you say?
Will you listen to my request? I'll pay you properly.
Yes
No
はい

\nc<Producer>Kuu... I knew it would come to this! I thought Saki-chan
would take on the job!

\nc<Producer>After all, you're a true perverted masochistic succubus who
gets excited even by illegal entry!

\nc<Producer>The favor is simple. You're doing promotional activities for
the First Succubus Industry, right? During that, I want you
to secretly spread our employee's business cards as well.

\nc<Producer>Worried about getting caught? No worries, no worries. I'll
take care of it.

\nc<Producer>We've seen Saki-chan's shining talent... You're more
reliable than leaving it to other succubi!
\nc<Producer>So, I'm counting on you.
いいえ

\nc<Producer>Is that so? Hmm... I thought it was a good idea. That's too
bad...
\nc<Producer>If you change your mind, come by anytime.
\nc<Producer>Please take care of the promotional activities.

\nc<>Gained the article on the mysterious string of
disappearances.
A
\nc<>Gained the "Succubus First Industry Media Guidelines".
A
